data.description: Experience the perfect combination of comfort and tranquility in this fabulous 3 bedroom, 3 bath home in the highly desired Northridge Subdivision. Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this home provides an ideal retreat for you and your loved ones. As you step inside the foyer, you'll immediately notice the large living room with cathedral ceilings and a cozy fireplace, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The bright kitchen has plenty of cabinet space, pantry and breakfast area for enjoying your morning coffee. There's also a separate dining room that's perfect for intimate dinners with family and friends. The large primary bedroom, located on the main level, is truly a dream featuring a spacious sitting area and en suite bathroom with a double vanity, soaking tub, and a walk-in tiled shower. An additional oversized bedroom with two separate closets can also be found on the main floor. The full finished basement is a true highlight of the home and ideal for unwinding in the large family room or getting a workout in the gym. You'll also find a bedroom, full bath with walk-in tiled shower, laundry room, and ample storage space. Recently updated features include a new roof and new interior paint, adding to the overall appeal of this already charming home. Sitting on a half-acre lot, the private fenced back yard is perfect for outdoor entertainment, while the elevated deck overlooking the back yard provides a beautiful view of nature. The 2 car garage is an added bonus, providing ample parking and storage. This home is perfect for those in search of a well-established neighborhood with numerous amenities including a clubhouse, swimming pool, tennis court, playground and more. Convenience to shopping, schools, entertainment, restaurants and I-475 is also a plus. Schedule a showing today and see for yourself all that this home has to offer!
